api.description:
The __FrameworkUtils__ contains useful functions and important prototypes. The __FrameworkUtils__ class is available in each node.js script according to the keyword `Utils.` (it’s a global variable):

```javascript
// Utils.[method]
Utils.trim({ name: '  PETER SIRKA  ' });
