methods.description:
Adds the error into the __ErrorBuilder__.

```javascript
var builder = new ErrorBuilder();

// Into the ErrorBuilder you can add the instance of ErrorBuilder.
instance.add(new builders.ErrorBuilder());

instance.add(‘name’, ‘@‘); // Gets the error message according to: instance.onResource(‘name');
// is same as
instance.add(‘name'); // Gets the error message according to: instance.onResource(‘name');

