## Isomorphic + F.merge() or F.map()

Filename on server-side: `/isomorphic/shared.js`:

```javascript
exports.getName = function() {
    // is_server == is a global variable
    // is_client == is a global variable
    return 'total.js' + (is_server ? ' (called from server)' : ' (called from client)');
};
```

`F.merge()` implementation with `#filename` (without .js extension):

```javascript
F.merge('/my-scripts.js', 'some-script1.js', 'some-script2.js', '#shared');
// or
F.map('/my-script.js', '#shared');
```
